<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>DUN</title>
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="DUN" />
  <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#423232" />
  <meta name="description" content="Legal document preparation for women who are done." />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 180 180'%3E%3Crect width='180' height='180' rx='40' fill='%23423232'/%3E%3Ctext x='90' y='125' font-family='Georgia,serif' font-size='96' font-weight='700' fill='%23BF8C8C' text-anchor='middle'%3ED%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" />
  <link rel="manifest" href="data:application/manifest+json,%7B%22name%22%3A%22DUN%22%2C%22short_name%22%3A%22DUN%22%2C%22start_url%22%3A%22%2F%22%2C%22display%22%3A%22standalone%22%2C%22background_color%22%3A%22%23423232%22%2C%22theme_color%22%3A%22%23423232%22%7D" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,700;1,400;1,500&family=Fredoka:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg: #423232; --card: #8A7272; --card-dark: #6B5555;
      --blush: #BF8C8C; --blush-lt: #D4AAAA;
      --text: #301212; --text-lt: #FCF2F2;
      --outline: #695151; --border: #7A6060;
      --safe-top: env(safe-area-inset-top,0px); --safe-bot: env(safe-area-inset-bottom,0px);
    }
    html,body { height:100%; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text); font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-weight:300; }
    #app { display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:100dvh; max-width:680px; margin:0 auto; padding-top:var(--safe-top); padding-bottom:var(--safe-bot); position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
    header { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:16px 20px 12px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--bg); flex-shrink:0; gap:12px; z-index:10; }
    .wordmark { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.12em; color:var(--blush); cursor:pointer; }
    .header-right { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
    .header-tag { font-size:10px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.6; }
    .safety-btn { background:transparent; border:1px solid #C0392B; border-radius:20px; padding:5px 12px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:11px; color:#E8A09A; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; white-space:nowrap; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
    .safety-btn:hover,.safety-btn:active { background:rgba(192,57,43,0.15); border-color:#E8A09A; }
    .tab-bar { display:flex; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--bg); flex-shrink:0; }
    .tab { flex:1; padding:11px 6px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:12px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.45; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; border-bottom:2px solid transparent; transition:all 0.2s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
    .tab.active { color:var(--blush); opacity:1; border-bottom-color:var(--blush); }
    .screen { display:none; flex:1; overflow-y:auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch; }
    .screen.active { display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
    .screen::-webkit-scrollbar { width:4px; }
    .screen::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background:var(--border); border-radius:2px; }
    #screen-home { padding:40px 24px 48px; align-items:center; text-align:center; }
    .home-eyebrow { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.24em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.6; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .home-headline { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:clamp(36px,9vw,54px); font-weight:400; line-height:1.05; color:var(--blush); margin-bottom:20px; }
    .home-headline em { font-style:italic; color:var(--blush-lt); }
    .home-pitch { font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.65; max-width:400px; margin-bottom:32px; opacity:0.9; }
    .home-pitch strong { font-weight:500; color:var(--blush-lt); }
    .divider { width:32px; height:1px; background:var(--blush); opacity:0.3; margin:0 auto 32px; }
    .three-things { width:100%; max-width:460px; margin-bottom:28px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; }
    .thing { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:16px; padding:16px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); text-align:left; }
    .thing:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .thing-num { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:400; color:var(--blush); opacity:0.5; flex-shrink:0; width:24px; padding-top:1px; }
    .thing-text { font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.55; }
    .thing-text strong { font-weight:500; color:var(--blush-lt); display:block; margin-bottom:2px; }
    .price-line { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:15px; font-style:italic; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.7; margin-bottom:32px; }
    .cta-btn { background:var(--blush); color:var(--text); border:none; border-radius:40px; padding:16px 40px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.06em; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .cta-btn:hover,.cta-btn:active { background:var(--blush-lt); transform:scale(0.98); }
    .cta-sub { font-size:12px; font-weight:300; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.5; margin-bottom:40px; }
    .devon-strip { width:100%; max-width:460px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); padding-top:28px; text-align:left; }
    .devon-strip-header { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:14px; }
    .devon-avatar { width:42px; height:42px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blush); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:var(--text); flex-shrink:0; }
    .devon-name { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:500; color:var(--blush-lt); }
    .devon-title { font-size:10px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); opacity:0.45; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:2px; }
    .devon-bio-text { font-size:13px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.7; opacity:0.75; }
    .devon-bio-text p + p { margin-top:10px; }
    .devon-sig { display:block; margin-top:12px; font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:14px; color:var(--blush); opacity:0.7; }
    #screen-chat { flex-direction:column; }
    #chat-messages { flex:1; overflow-y:auto; padding:0 20px; scroll-behavior:smooth; -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch; }
    #chat-messages::-webkit-scrollbar { width:4px; }
    #chat-messages::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background:var(--border); border-radius:2px; }
    .chat-welcome { padding:32px 0 20px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; text-align:center; }
    .chat-welcome-head { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:22px; font-weight:400; color:var(--blush); margin-bottom:8px; }
    .chat-welcome-sub { font-size:13px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); opacity:0.55; line-height:1.6; max-width:320px; margin-bottom:28px; }
    .chips { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; width:100%; }
    .chip { background:transparent; border:1px solid var(--outline); border-radius:40px; padding:11px 18px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); text-align:left; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; line-height:1.4; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
    .chip:hover,.chip:active { background:var(--card); border-color:var(--blush); }
    .messages-inner { padding:16px 0 12px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:18px; }
    .msg { display:flex; gap:10px; animation:fadeUp 0.3s ease both; }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
    .msg.user { flex-direction:row-reverse; }
    .avatar { width:28px; height:28px; border-radius:50%; flex-shrink:0; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-top:2px; }
    .avatar.dun { background:var(--blush); color:var(--text); font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; }
    .avatar.you { background:var(--card-dark); border:1px solid var(--outline); color:var(--blush-lt); font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:8px; letter-spacing:0.08em; }
    .bubble { max-width:85%; font-size:14.5px; font-weight:300; line-height:1.65; }
    .msg.user .bubble { background:var(--card); color:var(--text-lt); padding:12px 16px; border-radius:18px 4px 18px 18px; }
    .msg.assistant .bubble { color:var(--text-lt); }
    .signature { display:block; margin-top:10px; font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:13px; color:var(--blush); opacity:0.8; }
    .typing-dots { display:flex; gap:5px; padding:12px 4px; align-items:center; }
    .typing-dots span { width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blush); opacity:0.5; animation:pulse 1.2s infinite; }
    .typing-dots span:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.2s} .typing-dots span:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.4s}
    @keyframes pulse{0%,80%,100%{transform:scale(0.8);opacity:0.35}40%{transform:scale(1.1);opacity:0.9}}
    #input-area { padding:12px 20px 14px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--bg); flex-shrink:0; }
    .input-wrap { display:flex; align-items:flex-end; gap:10px; background:var(--card-dark); border:1px solid var(--outline); border-radius:32px; padding:10px 10px 10px 18px; transition:border-color 0.2s; }
    .input-wrap:focus-within { border-color:var(--blush); }
    textarea { flex:1; background:transparent; border:none; outline:none; resize:none; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.5; min-height:22px; max-height:130px; overflow-y:auto; }
    textarea::placeholder { color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.45; }
    .send-btn { width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blush); border:none; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.1s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
    .send-btn:hover{background:var(--blush-lt)} .send-btn:active{transform:scale(0.93)} .send-btn:disabled{background:var(--outline);cursor:default}
    .disclaimer { text-align:center; font-size:10px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.35; letter-spacing:0.06em; margin-top:8px; }
    #scroll-anchor{height:1px}
    #screen-info { padding:32px 24px 48px; }
    .info-section { margin-bottom:32px; }
    .info-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blush-lt); opacity:0.5; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .info-heading { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:24px; font-weight:400; color:var(--blush); margin-bottom:12px; line-height:1.2; }
    .info-body { font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.7; opacity:0.85; }
    .info-body p + p { margin-top:10px; }
    .info-divider { height:1px; background:var(--border); margin:28px 0; }
    .info-cta { display:block; background:var(--blush); color:var(--text); border:none; border-radius:40px; padding:15px 32px; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:500; letter-spacing:0.06em; cursor:pointer; text-align:center; text-decoration:none; transition:all 0.2s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; margin-top:8px; }
    .info-cta:hover,.info-cta:active { background:var(--blush-lt); }
    .info-cta.outline { background:transparent; border:1px solid var(--outline); color:var(--blush-lt); margin-top:10px; }
    .info-cta.outline:hover { border-color:var(--blush); color:var(--blush); }
    .confidential-note { background:var(--card-dark); border:1px solid var(--outline); border-radius:12px; padding:16px 18px; margin-top:16px; font-size:13px; font-weight:300; color:var(--text-lt); line-height:1.65; opacity:0.85; }
    .confidential-note strong { font-weight:500; color:var(--blush-lt); display:block; margin-bottom:4px; }
    #safety-screen { display:none; position:absolute; inset:0; background:#1A0A0A; z-index:100; flex-direction:column; padding-top:var(--safe-top); }
    #safety-screen.visible { display:flex; }
    .safety-header { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:20px 24px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid #3A1A1A; }
    .safety-header-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:400; color:#E8A09A; }
    .safety-close { background:none; border:none; color:#8B5050; cursor:pointer; font-size:22px; padding:0; line-height:1; }
    .safety-body { flex:1; overflow-y:auto; padding:28px 24px; }
    .safety-top-line { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:clamp(22px,6vw,30px); font-weight:400; color:#FCF2F2; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .safety-sub { font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#C4A0A0; line-height:1.65; margin-bottom:32px; }
    .safety-resource { display:flex; flex-direction:column; border:1px solid #3A1A1A; border-radius:12px; padding:18px 20px; margin-bottom:12px; background:#221010; text-decoration:none; transition:border-color 0.2s; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent; }
    .safety-resource:active { border-color:#C0392B; }
    .safety-resource-label { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#8B5050; margin-bottom:5px; }
    .safety-resource-title { font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:400; color:#E8A09A; margin-bottom:3px; }
    .safety-resource-desc { font-size:13px; font-weight:300; color:#C4A0A0; line-height:1.5; }
    .safety-resource.emergency { border-color:#7A2020; }
    .safety-resource.emergency .safety-resource-title { font-size:22px; }
    .safety-divider-text { text-align:center; font-size:11px; color:#5A3030; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; margin:8px 0 18px; }
    .safety-note { font-size:12px; color:#6B4040; line-height:1.6; text-align:center; margin-top:20px; border-top:1px solid #2A1010; padding-top:18px; }
    .safety-continue { background:none; border:1px solid #3A1A1A; border-radius:40px; padding:12px 24px; margin-top:14px; width:100%; font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#8B6060; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; }
    .safety-continue:hover,.safety-continue:active { border-color:#6B4040; color:#C4A0A0; }
    #install-banner{display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:10px 20px;background:var(--card);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);gap:12px;flex-shrink:0}
    #install-banner.visible{display:flex}
    .install-text{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--text-lt);line-height:1.4}
    .install-text strong{font-weight:500;color:var(--blush-lt)}
    .install-btn{background:var(--blush);color:var(--text);border:none;border-radius:20px;padding:7px 16px;font-family:'Fredoka',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
    .install-dismiss{background:none;border:none;color:var(--blush-lt);opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer;font-size:18px;padding:0 4px}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="app">
  <div id="safety-screen">
    <div class="safety-header">
      <div class="safety-header-title">Your safety comes first.</div>
      <button class="safety-close" onclick="closeSafety()">&#x2715;</button>
    </div>
    <div class="safety-body">
      <div class="safety-top-line">Are you able to speak freely right now?</div>
      <div class="safety-sub">If there is any chance your device is being monitored, these resources are free, confidential, and available any time.</div>
      <a class="safety-resource emergency" href="tel:911"><div class="safety-resource-label">Emergency</div><div class="safety-resource-title">Call 911</div><div class="safety-resource-desc">If you are in immediate danger, call now.</div></a>
      <div class="safety-divider-text">or reach a trained advocate</div>
      <a class="safety-resource" href="tel:18007997233"><div class="safety-resource-label">National Domestic Violence Hotline</div><div class="safety-resource-title">1-800-799-7233</div><div class="safety-resource-desc">Call or text 24/7. Free and confidential.</div></a>
      <a class="safety-resource" href="https://www.thehotline.org/get-help/hotline-chat/" target="_blank"><div class="safety-resource-label">Prefer to chat?</div><div class="safety-resource-title">thehotline.org</div><div class="safety-resource-desc">Live chat if you cannot speak safely.</div></a>
      <a class="safety-resource" href="sms:741741&body=START"><div class="safety-resource-label">Crisis Text Line</div><div class="safety-resource-title">Text HOME to 741741</div><div class="safety-resource-desc">Free, 24/7 support by text.</div></a>
      <div class="safety-note">Tap the X to leave this screen quickly. Your conversation is still here when you are ready.</div>
      <button class="safety-continue" onclick="closeSafety()">I am safe. Take me back.</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header>
    <div class="wordmark" onclick="showTab('home')">DUN</div>
    <div class="header-right">
      <button class="safety-btn" onclick="openSafety()">Are you safe?</button>
      <div class="header-tag">Not legal advice</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div id="install-banner">
    <div class="install-text"><strong>Add DUN to your home screen</strong> for instant access.</div>
    <button class="install-btn" id="install-btn">Add</button>
    <button class="install-dismiss" id="install-dismiss">x</button>
  </div>

  <div class="tab-bar">
    <button class="tab active" id="tab-home" onclick="showTab('home')">Home</button>
    <button class="tab" id="tab-chat" onclick="showTab('chat')">Ask Devon</button>
    <button class="tab" id="tab-info" onclick="showTab('info')">How It Works</button>
  </div>

  <div class="screen active" id="screen-home">
    <div class="home-eyebrow">You found the right place.</div>
    <h1 class="home-headline">You're here because<br/>you're <em>done.</em></h1>
    <p class="home-pitch">Tell me what's going on in your own words.<br/><strong>I'll tell you exactly how I can help.</strong></p>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="three-things">
      <div class="thing"><div class="thing-num">1</div><div class="thing-text"><strong>We listen. And we believe you.</strong>Every situation is different. You talk, I listen — no judgment, no time limit.</div></div>
      <div class="thing"><div class="thing-num">2</div><div class="thing-text"><strong>We give you a plan.</strong>A detailed outline of exactly what you need, in what order, and why.</div></div>
      <div class="thing"><div class="thing-num">3</div><div class="thing-text"><strong>We do the paperwork.</strong>Contract, deposit, and we prepare every document for you. You show up ready.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="price-line">Most cases average $500 to $1,000.</div>
    <a class="cta-btn" href="TALLY_FORM_URL_HERE" target="_blank">I'm Ready</a>
    <div class="cta-sub">No commitment. Just a conversation.</div>
    <div class="devon-strip">
      <div class="devon-strip-header">
        <div class="devon-avatar">D</div>
        <div><div class="devon-name">Devon Dun</div><div class="devon-title">Founder, DUN</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="devon-bio-text">
        <p>I built DUN from inside the system — seven years of court dates, documents, and filings. Every moment of confusion the process is designed to create, I have been there.</p>
        <p>I spent those years building something useful: the knowledge, the tools, and the relationships with attorneys and legal professionals who believe every woman deserves to walk into a courtroom prepared.</p>
        <p>I have been exactly where you are. I am still there right now. I am just sharing every tool I have found so you can be DUN a lot sooner than I am.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="devon-sig">— Devon Dun</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen" id="screen-chat">
    <div id="chat-messages">
      <div class="chat-welcome">
        <div class="chat-welcome-head">Ask me anything.</div>
        <div class="chat-welcome-sub">Divorce, custody, orders of protection, court process — nothing is off limits. Start anywhere.</div>
        <div class="chips">
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">I don't even know where to start.</button>
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">What does uncontested actually mean?</button>
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">He just served me papers. Now what?</button>
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">I feel like I'm always the problem.</button>
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">I need to understand my custody options.</button>
          <button class="chip" onclick="sendSuggestion(this)">What is an order of protection?</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="messages-inner" id="messages"></div>
      <div id="scroll-anchor"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="input-area">
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <textarea id="input" rows="1" placeholder="Ask anything..." onkeydown="handleKey(event)" oninput="autoResize(this)"></textarea>
        <button class="send-btn" id="send-btn" onclick="send()" title="Send">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M7 12V2M2 7l5-5 5 5" stroke="#301212" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="disclaimer">DUN is a document preparation service, not a law firm. Nothing here is legal advice.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="screen" id="screen-info">
    <div class="info-section">
      <div class="info-label">What DUN does</div>
      <div class="info-heading">Stop worrying about whether you can afford the right support. Start making sure you're getting it.</div>
      <div class="info-body"><p>DUN prepares legal documents for women who are self-represented or working alongside an attorney. Divorce, legal separation, custody agreements, parenting plans, child support worksheets, orders of protection, and full court document organization.</p><p>You do not need to know what any of that means yet. That is what the first conversation is for.</p></div>
