    <div class="info-divider"></div>
    <div class="info-section">
      <div class="info-label">How it works</div>
      <div class="info-heading">Three steps. No surprises.</div>
      <div class="info-body"><p><strong style="color:var(--blush-lt)">You tell me what's going on.</strong> In your own words. I read every word personally.</p><p><strong style="color:var(--blush-lt)">I send you a plan and a price.</strong> A clear outline of what you need and what it costs. No commitment until you are ready.</p><p><strong style="color:var(--blush-lt)">We get to work.</strong> Contract, deposit, and we handle every document. You focus on your life.</p></div>
